targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  lending_rates.time,
  lending_rates.venue || ':' || lending_rates.token AS text,
  lending_rates.rate * 24 * 365 * 100 AS rate
FROM lending_rates
WHERE
  lending_rates.venue IN ($venue)
  AND lending_rates.token IN ($token)
ORDER BY lending_rates.time

SELECT
  NOW() - interval '4 hours' AS time,
  venue || ':' || token AS text,
  AVG(rate) * 24 * 365 * 100 AS rate
FROM lending_rates
WHERE
  time >= NOW() - interval '4 hours'
  AND token = 'usd'
GROUP BY venue, token
